{"tid":2439411,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"電影《理大圍城》首登商營戲院— 高先電影院","createTime":"2021-03-09T08:48:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T12:37:28.000Z","uid":303304,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"577bb250030e85bd79addacb8717e1720086ed16","tid":2439411,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T08:48:20.000Z","msg":"高先電影院今日在Facebook 宣布，將於本月中舉辦「香港電影評論學會大獎 - 得獎電影巡禮」，播放各部得獎電影，包括：《理大圍城》、《奪冠》、《夜香．鴛鴦．深水埗》、《好好拍電影》、《3cm》以及《一秒拳王》。門票將於明日（10日）早上10點在HKMovie App上公開發售。每部電影完場後將設15分鐘影評人出席映後談，包括譚以諾、李焯桃、曾肇弘等。<br />\n<br />\n六部得獎電影巡禮作品中，只有《理大圍城》一直未有商業影院願意放映，這次高先電影院或成首間播放《理大圍城》的商營戲院。有網民在高先電影院FB留言要求加場，指「理大圍城得一場 &hellip; 唔得，點搶呀」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/culture/高先戲院播電影評論學會得獎作-理大圍城-首登商營戲院/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%E9%AB%98%E5%85%88%E6%88%B2%E9%99%A2%E6%92%AD%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1%E8%A9%95%E8%AB%96%E5%AD%B8%E6%9C%83%E5%BE%97%E7%8D%8E%E4%BD%9C-%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7%E5%9C%8D%E5%9F%8E-%E9%A6%96%E7%99%BB%E5%95%86%E7%87%9F%E6%88%B2%E9%99%A2%2F&d=eGp%2FCvHI00KNC8mlo1Mhy5IBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=3e4ada73\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%E9%AB%98%E5%85%88%E6%88%B2%E9%99%A2%E6%92%AD%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1%E8%A9%95%E8%AB%96%E5%AD%B8%E6%9C%83%E5%BE%97%E7%8D%8E%E4%BD%9C-%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7%E5%9C%8D%E5%9F%8E-%E9%A6%96%E7%99%BB%E5%95%86%E7%87%9F%E6%88%B2%E9%99%A2%2F&h=b8dd413f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/culture/高先戲院播電影評論學會得獎作-理大圍城-首登商營戲院/</a>"},{"pid":"80c9311b62ed1610d0f8444d3e12e3b068aa2a68","tid":2439411,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T08:49:08.000Z","msg":"獲學會評為最佳電影的《理大圍城》過去曾於香港藝術中心放映。<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"gold\">這次將會是該片首次登上商營戲院。</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"deb5c41e62d46cd67ef56fa65353f6a656fac7f4","tid":2439411,"uid":303304,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-